{"id":14248,"date":"2023-03-22T16:01:14","date_gmt":"2023-03-22T09:01:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=14248"},"modified":"2023-03-22T16:01:14","modified_gmt":"2023-03-22T09:01:14","slug":"sac-khong-day-cho-xe-dien-sap-thanh-hien-thuc-con-de-hon-ca-sac-dien-thoai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/sac-khong-day-cho-xe-dien-sap-thanh-hien-thuc-con-de-hon-ca-sac-dien-thoai\/","title":{"rendered":"S\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y cho xe \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1eafp th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 s\u1ea1c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<h2 class=\"detail-sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\">Vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i xe \u0111i\u1ec7n Hyundai Ioniq 5 v\u1edbi tr\u1ea1m s\u1ea1c th\u00f4ng qua d\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh d\u0129 v\u00e3ng.<\/h2>\n<div data-check-position=\"body_start\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"detail-cmain\">\n<div class=\"detail-content afcbc-body\" data-role=\"content\">\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\/471584752817336320\/2023\/3\/9\/xe-dien-hyundai-sac-khong-day1-16783536562771471189598.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-fancybox=\"content\" data-caption=\"Xe \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1eafm d\u00e2y \u0111i\u1ec7n l\u1eb1ng nh\u1eb1ng n\u1eefa - \u1ea2nh: Hyundai\"><img decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_558218490977927168\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"S\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y cho xe \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1eafp th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 s\u1ea1c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i - \u1ea2nh 1.\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\/thumb_w\/730\/471584752817336320\/2023\/3\/9\/xe-dien-hyundai-sac-khong-day1-16783536562771471189598.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y cho xe \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1eafp th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 s\u1ea1c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i - \u1ea2nh 1.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\/471584752817336320\/2023\/3\/9\/xe-dien-hyundai-sac-khong-day1-16783536562771471189598.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<div id=\"wrapper-inimage-pos-sponsor-0\">\n<div id=\"in-images\">\n<div id=\"zone-joqxux31\">\n<div id=\"share-joqxuxkg\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p class=\"\" data-placeholder=\"[nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch]\">Xe \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1eafm d\u00e2y \u0111i\u1ec7n l\u1eb1ng nh\u1eb1ng n\u1eefa &#8211; \u1ea2nh: Hyundai<\/p>\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Theo\u00a0<i>Carbuzz<\/i>,\u00a0<a class=\"link-inline-content\" title=\"Hyundai\" href=\"https:\/\/tuoitre.vn\/hyundai.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-rel=\"follow\">Hyundai<\/a>\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed9p \u0111\u01a1n xin c\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng s\u00e1ng ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 s\u1ea1c xe \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y l\u00ean V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng S\u1edf h\u1eefu tr\u00ed tu\u1ec7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (KIPO).<\/p>\n<p>H\u00ecnh dung \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c\u00a0<a class=\"link-inline-content\" title=\"S\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y\" href=\"https:\/\/tuoitre.vn\/sac-khong-day.html\" data-rel=\"follow\">s\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y<\/a>\u00a0v\u1edbi xe \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y th\u00f4ng qua \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eeb, \u0111\u1ec3 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ebf s\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 thu (\u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i). C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u thu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn cu\u1ed9n d\u00e2y qu\u1ea5n quanh c\u00e1c l\u00f5i ferit (l\u00f5i xuy\u1ebfn, l\u00f5i t\u1eeb t\u00ednh) ri\u00eang l\u1ebb. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n \u0111i\u1ec7n, s\u1ebd h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng xung quanh \u0111\u1ebf s\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\n<p>Hyundai tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y cho xe \u0111i\u1ec7n h\u01a1n l\u00e0 smartphone. Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 s\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p>C\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 d\u00e2y cu\u1ed9n. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb s\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y hi\u1ec7n nay s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i d\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed3ng Litz. D\u00e2y n\u00e0y c\u1ef1c m\u1ecfng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t ch\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng gian. Nh\u01b0ng Litz ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0 smartphone. N\u1ebfu \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0o ng\u00e0nh \u00f4 t\u00f4, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt l\u1ea1i ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn chi ph\u00ed c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf.<\/p>\n<p><a class=\"VCCTagItemInNews\" title=\"C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi\" href=\"https:\/\/tuoitre.vn\/cong-nghe-moi.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-zoneid=\"0\" data-id=\"0\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi<\/a>\u00a0c\u1ee7a Hyundai kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u00e2y Litz, m\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t d\u00e2y ph\u1eb3ng (kh\u00f4ng b\u1ec7n xo\u1eafn nh\u01b0 Litz) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1m s\u00e1t l\u00f5i ferit. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y cho ph\u00e9p cu\u1ed9n nhi\u1ec1u d\u00e2y h\u01a1n v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ec3 t\u00edch nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i b\u1edbt ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n. Lo\u1ea1i d\u00e2y n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1m s\u00e1t c\u00e1c g\u00f3c vu\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bo tr\u00f2n c\u1ee7a l\u00f5i ferit, gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u1ea3m t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\n<div id=\"InreadPc\">\n<div id=\"zone-jnvk0c1v\">\n<div id=\"share-jnvk0cro\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\/471584752817336320\/2023\/3\/9\/xe-dien-hyundai-sac-khong-day6-16783537225571144394134.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-fancybox=\"content\" data-caption=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 xin c\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng s\u00e1ng ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Hyundai - \u1ea2nh: KIPO\"><img decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_558218768368222208\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"S\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y cho xe \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1eafp th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 s\u1ea1c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i - \u1ea2nh 2.\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\/thumb_w\/730\/471584752817336320\/2023\/3\/9\/xe-dien-hyundai-sac-khong-day6-16783537225571144394134.jpg\" alt=\"S\u1ea1c kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y cho xe \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1eafp th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 s\u1ea1c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i - \u1ea2nh 2.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\/471584752817336320\/2023\/3\/9\/xe-dien-hyundai-sac-khong-day6-16783537225571144394134.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/div><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p class=\"\" data-placeholder=\"[nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch]\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 xin c\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng s\u00e1ng ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Hyundai &#8211; \u1ea2nh: KIPO<\/p>\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>C\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m chi ph\u00ed, n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec7n, cho ph\u00e9p t\u1ea1o ra t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eafm ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0o xe ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111i v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng gian \u201c\u0111\u1ebf s\u1ea1c\u201d, ch\u1edd xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u201cc\u1eafm\u201d tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o \u201c\u0111\u1ebf\u201d nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ec3 s\u1ea1c ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebf sao cho m\u1eb7t ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac kh\u1edbp nhau. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c do l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed\u00a0<a class=\"VCCTagItemInNews\" title=\"b\u1ee9c x\u1ea1 \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eeb\" href=\"https:\/\/tuoitre.vn\/buc-xa-dien-tu.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-zoneid=\"0\" data-id=\"0\">b\u1ee9c x\u1ea1 \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eeb<\/a>\u00a0qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t truy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3m.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i n\u1eefa l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Hyundai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t ngay trong garage nh\u00e0 hay b\u00e3i \u0111\u1eadu xe c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng, cho ph\u00e9p xe \u0111i\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed7 v\u00e0o \u00f4 nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ea1p \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7.<\/p>\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n: tuoitre.vn<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i xe \u0111i\u1ec7n Hyundai Ioniq 5 v\u1edbi tr\u1ea1m s\u1ea1c th\u00f4ng qua d\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh d\u0129 v\u00e3ng. Xe \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i c\u1eafm d\u00e2y \u0111i\u1ec7n l\u1eb1ng nh\u1eb1ng n\u1eefa &#8211; \u1ea2nh: Hyundai Theo\u00a0Carbuzz,\u00a0Hyundai\u00a0\u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed9p \u0111\u01a1n xin c\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng s\u00e1ng ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 s\u1ea1c xe \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng d\u00e2y l\u00ean [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14248"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14248"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14248\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":14249,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14248\/revisions\/14249"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14248"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=14248"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=14248"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?post=14248"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}